                Egen forplejning, High5 energidrik, kildevand og banan
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-4 text-base md:text-lg font-instrument text-orange-700 text-left">17,5 KM</td>
              <td class="py-4 text-base md:text-lg font-instrument text-orange-700 text-center">Højre</td>
              <td class="py-4 text-base md:text-lg font-instrument text-orange-700 text-right">
                High5 energidrik og kildevand
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-4 text-base md:text-lg font-instrument text-orange-700 text-left">20 KM</td>
